    "causal_summary": "The Spec-Kit Memory MCP fuses five channels (vector, FTS5, BM25, causal-graph, degree) via RRF with FSRS power-law decay, but has no query-class routing, uses flag-based fact currentness, blocks on synchronous consolidation, and does not guarantee deterministic recall serialization. The external systems encode mature alternatives to each.",
